						 <p>Very 'cool', +1.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>If I understand the skip correctly, I like the suggestion that something very hot was using -B to enter the room since -A was found burning a hole in the floor, and the interest that makes combined with the note is neat. Wonder what it was.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
